kpi.name: cds_611a

kpi_info.title: Minimum free circuits in the circuit group
kpi_info.use:
Minimum number of free circuits in the circuit group during the measurement period.

This KPI is similar to msc_611a. New KPI ID reference (CDS NE). This new KPI ID reference is to to be used starting from M15.1 report sets.
